{"tid":1555821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] 有個奇難雜症希望各位巴打比少少意見","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T06:22:51.000Z","uid":22234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"56a3397979bbd9aeab6b77c0d1b97212f8b8f645","tid":1555821,"uid":22234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的，部ＰＳ４大概三個月無開，近排芒亨更新，一開就出事。<br />\n<br />\n唔插ＨＤＭＩ正常開機，藍燈轉白燈，一插ＨＤＭＩ就會即刻熄機，直頭係條ＨＤＭＩ線掂到個插頭（未插入去）就即刻熄個隻。<br />\n<br />\n試過換ＨＤＭＩ線，試過換其他電視，連條power supply線都換過第2條試，結果一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n有時唔知點解好彩可以開機玩一陣，時間唔定，半個鐘～３個鐘之後又會自動熄機。<br />\n<br />\n情況有少少似搶電。<br />\n<br />\n問過整底板要７８０＄<br />\n<br />\n網上有Ｄ唔拆機既方法，例如抆曬所有線３０秒後再插返、長按７秒。。等等都試過<br />\n<br />\n請問各位有無試過同樣情況，細佬我唔識機械野，有無巴打知大概可以點整？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab7e195370595ef7407b62e8c50aadf20aa2b9f","tid":1555821,"uid":22234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"補充返少少<br />\n<br />\n上面話有時得，但其實９０％既嘗試都係<br />\n<br />\n＂唔插ＨＤＭＩ正常開機，藍燈轉白燈，一插ＨＤＭＩ就會即刻熄機，直頭係條ＨＤＭＩ線掂到個插頭（未插入去）就即刻熄個隻。＂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過左保養，所以唔打算送返比ｓｏｎｙ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj